description.narrative: In 2021, Egypt Country Office had met its KPI scorecard indicator areas except for people management recruitment speed. Office processes and SOPS were developed and revised for more efficient and efficient planning and management of programs. Guidelines and Capacity building to ECO staff were provided in lieu of the new CPD and UNSDCF development. Monitoring: partnership reporting and PSEA assessments- prevention and response were held and have continued to strengthen ECO RBM functions.;The operationalization of E-tools was further capacitated with more emphasis on partnership reporting. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:03/01/2022
